OL,3,CThief caught on CCTV making chocolate
OL,4,Cegg raid jailed
OL,6,FCCTV footage released by Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice captured Callum Little leaving
OL,8,Fa trail of chocolate eggs behind as he
OL,9,Fmade off with a shop display
OL,11,FA sweet-toothed shoplifter who was
OL,12,Fcaught on camera stealing chocolate
OL,13,Feggs in Gateshead has been jailed.
OL,15,FCCTV footage shows Callum Little, 27,
OL,16,Fpicking up a display of Creme Eggs
OL,17,Ffrom a shop before running through the
OL,18,Fdoors, leaving a trail of dozens of
OL,19,Fchocolate eggs behind him.
