OL,3,CThief caught on CCTV making chocolate
OL,4,Cegg raid jailed
OL,6,FThe theft was part of a a
OL,7,Ffiveandahalfweek crime spree
OL,8,Fcarried out by Little across stores in
OL,9,Fthe Wrekenton, Low Fell and Beacon
OL,10,FLough areas, Northumbria Police said.
OL,12,FLittle, of no fixed abode, took items
OL,13,Fincluding sweets, meat and dairy
OL,14,Fproducts from the shops from New Year
OL,15,Fonwards until he was arrested on
OL,16,FFriday 13 February.
OL,18,FHe was charged with 18 counts of
OL,19,Fshoplifting and the following day, he
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to all offences at
OL,21,FNewcastle Crown Court.
